{"tid":993394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女病人因姦成孕 警拘療養院男護 圖","createTime":"2019-01-24T01:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T02:36:25.000Z","uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d5057d8093221b47ded54165678dbea0d9086b1b","tid":993394,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"美國亞利桑那州鳳凰城植物人誕子案，一名36歲療養院護士被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方周三指，測試證實薩瑟蘭（Nathan Sutherland）的DNA與植物人嬰兒的吻合後，將他拘捕，控告他一項性侵及一項虐待弱勢成人罪。<br />\n<br />\n警方指薩瑟蘭拒絕對話。療養院表示，性侵事件發生期間，薩瑟蘭正是負責照顧受害人的護士，已經將他解僱。<br />\n<br />\n29歲受害人3歲時遇溺後失去活動能力，之後一直入住哈辛達療養院（Hacienda HealthCare），上月29日誕下男嬰。警方懷疑她因姦成孕，於是展開調查，收集療養院內所有男職員的DNA，與嬰兒的進行對比。<br />\n<br />\n療養院周日宣佈，一名負責照顧女受害人的醫生已經辭職，另一名醫生則被停職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190124/59177993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190124%2F59177993&d=pWeF2krRNNBkkT%2F01MMq%2Bcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=1a0200e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190124%2F59177993&h=1441013a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190124/59177993</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190124/large/1548266073_0804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190124%2Flarge%2F1548266073_0804.jpg&h=a4810708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣衰，已經揾到犯案原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cd47be8eb1b9a830e715061675f7c7980917ab","tid":993394,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:51:19.000Z","msg":"植物人都搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c2ce9ba75037701582673cadffdd4f8291a5af","tid":993394,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"